config CONFIG_MSM_THREAD_POWER
	tristate "MSM Thread Power Control"
	depends on ARCH_QCOM
	help
		MSM Thread Power control driver.
		This provides a parameter to switch on/off power from PMIC
		to Thread device. This will control LDOs/Clock/GPIOs to
		control Thread Chipset based on power on/off sequence.

		Say Y here to compile support for Thread Power driver
		into the kernel or say M to compile as a module.
